**Thank you for becoming a member of the Manchester YMCA Harriers!**

You can order club kit using the buttons below.

You can collect any kit you order at our Thursday evening club runs, or otherwise by [getting in touch with us](/contact).

### A note on sizing

The general consensus is that our kit is loose-fitting for the size specified; if your like your kit to be a bit of a tighter fit, order a size smaller than you normally would.

## Current kit

Are you a fan of the latest fashion trends?

This is the latest edition of our club kit, complete with our fancy Manchester YMCA Harriers branding.  It's all the rage in Milan!

**Note:** We will be placing an order with our kit supplier on **28th September** - any order you place now should be with you in a few weeks! If you order after this date, it may be a long time before you receive your kit... you've been warned!

